cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.CV

The paper proposes a method for certifying causal fairness of feed-forward neural networks used for classification tasks. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The concern about bias in machine learning models also relates to computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) and cybernetics (cs.CY). Additionally, the use of neural networks for classification tasks suggests a potential application in computer vision (cs.CV).
